    {
      "height": 320,
      "id": "0424dba68c2be4de",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Floating above the clouds\nThere is a big valley between the city and suburbs created by city architects for its beauty.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 580,
      "x": -360,
      "y": -500
    },
    {
      "color": "5",
      "height": 275,
      "id": "05fb7ce93f9eca77",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "border": "dashed",
        "shape": null
      },
      "text": "Battery partially flooded. Water level manipulated to solve. Puzzle includes power sources and light bridges. Floaties not required until after this puzzle.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 380,
      "x": 380,
      "y": -55
    },
    {
      "color": "4",
      "height": 80,
      "id": "a7c66f9b83f13cf6",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Light bridge intermediate",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": 180,
      "y": 600
    },
    {
      "height": 360,
      "id": "1ddb8df3d186f59d",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "border": "dashed"
      },
      "text": "Puzzle makes player think about how the light bridges are connected, has to make steps in the proper order.\n\n(could get annoying)\n(is that all there is to this room?)",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 400,
      "x": 120,
      "y": 900
    },
    {
      "height": 360,
      "id": "2aaf2f999ebd1d70",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Pitstop\n\nhas car park, electric refuel, gas refuel,\n\ninterior is what has pool area",
      "type": "text",
