      "styleAttributes": {
        "border": "dashed"
      },
      "text": "Player walks out to runway, there is a \"ramp\" with traffic leading out of the city, and a gate/checkpoint tunnel for gaining access to the walking path.\n\nOnce on the walking path, light bridges are introduced in a safe manner before suspending the player over a large drop.",
